.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH codeaegis 1  "codeaegis " 
.SH NAME
codeaegis \- CodeAegis Security Scanner & MCP Server
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcodeaegis\fR [\fB\-\-logs\fR] [\fB\-m\fR|\fB\-\-model\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
CodeAegis Security Scanner & MCP Server
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-logs\fR
Enable quality logging for scan results and critic decisions
.TP
\fB\-m\fR, \fB\-\-model\fR \fI<MODEL>\fR
Override the LLM model to use
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
codeaegis\-mcp(1)
Runs the CodeAegis MCP Server
.TP
codeaegis\-watch(1)
Monitors a directory for file changes and scans them automatically
.TP
codeaegis\-lsp(1)
Runs the CodeAegis Language Server (LSP)
.TP
codeaegis\-scan(1)
Scans a directory for vulnerabilities
.TP
codeaegis\-auth(1)
Manage LLM authentication credentials in the OS keychain
.TP
codeaegis\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
